1
00:00:25,250 --> 00:00:32,210
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="33"><font face="Georgia"><font color="#9eccf8">Beyond Journey's End</font></font></font></b></font>

2
00:01:29,990 --> 00:01:32,990
<font face="Times New Roman">{\an7}<font color="#f7fffa">Episode 36: A Magnificent End</font></font>

3
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As I thought, this won't be easy.</i></font>

4
00:02:20,940 --> 00:02:25,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's like fighting multiple 
master swordsmen at once.</i></font>

5
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>On top of the sheer number of attacks,</i></font>

6
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>his reflexes and stamina 
far exceed human levels.</i></font>

7
00:02:31,980 --> 00:02:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stark is being overpowered.</i></font>

8
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:37,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If this becomes a battle 
of endurance, we're sure to lose.</i></font>

9
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Should we retreat and regroup?</i></font>

10
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, he's faster than us. 
He'd chase us down.</i></font>

11
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is bad. Frieren was right.</i></font>

12
00:02:51,230 --> 00:02:53,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't read his attacks.</i></font>

13
00:02:55,330 --> 00:02:56,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In that case...</i></font>

14
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fool. I told him not to 
take his attacks head-on.</i></font>

15
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are mine.</font>

16
00:03:08,110 --> 00:03:10,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He let himself get cut on purpose?</i></font>

17
00:03:10,430 --> 00:03:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's one tough kid.</i></font>

18
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:21,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stark, you're a skilled warrior.</font>

19
00:03:21,870 --> 00:03:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You created the slight opening I needed.</font>

20
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's over, Revolte.</font>

21
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. I remember now.</font>

22
00:03:40,110 --> 00:03:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the partner of the 
first-class mage I killed before.</font>

23
00:03:45,270 --> 00:03:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I recall the situation 
was similar to this one.</font>

24
00:03:48,370 --> 00:03:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd gone off to slay other demons, 
while your partner defended the village.</font>

25
00:03:54,830 --> 00:04:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the time you returned, it was too late.</font>

26
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you want to know 
how your partner died?</font>

27
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:04,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silence.</font>

28
00:04:05,140 --> 00:04:09,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I learned a truly interesting 
lesson from that battle.</font>

29
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough. I'll silence you myself.</font>

30
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I have one last 
piece of advice for you.</font>

31
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should check more 
thoroughly for survivors.</font>

32
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:25,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A child?</font>

33
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just delaying the inevitable.</font>

34
00:04:47,110 --> 00:04:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it! I did it, Lord Revolte!</font>

35
00:04:50,820 --> 00:04:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Praise—</font>

36
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well done. You have my thanks.</font>

37
00:05:00,710 --> 00:05:02,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My judgment was clouded.</i></font>

38
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:05,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For a moment, 
all I could think of was him.</i></font>

39
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew there couldn't be a child here.</i></font>

40
00:05:12,670 --> 00:05:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was right. Humans have a habit 
of protecting their young.</font>

41
00:05:21,270 --> 00:05:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do we?</font>

42
00:05:23,030 --> 00:05:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that were true, the world 
would be a more peaceful place.</font>

43
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only ever knew one idiot who died 
protecting a child he didn't know.</font>

44
00:05:39,610 --> 00:05:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps he was too kind.</font>

45
00:05:44,050 --> 00:05:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the same in every era.</font>

46
00:05:46,710 --> 00:05:49,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kind mages don't live long.</font>

47
00:05:50,020 --> 00:05:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He met a magnificent end.</font>

48
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So even you say things you don't mean.</font>

49
00:05:57,970 --> 00:06:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Genau, you're an unpleasant man.</font>

50
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have a shred of kindness.</font>

51
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay that way forever.</font>

52
00:06:13,410 --> 00:06:14,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you wish.</font>

53
00:06:16,230 --> 00:06:20,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do not enjoy killing.</font>

54
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall put you out of your misery.</font>

55
00:06:24,420 --> 00:06:28,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shouldn't have acted out of character.</font>

56
00:06:37,250 --> 00:06:38,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm surprised.</font>

57
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't think there was a warrior alive 
who could stop a direct hit from me.</font>

58
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can still move? 
You should've played dead.</font>

59
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we would've lost.</font>

60
00:06:55,380 --> 00:07:00,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Battles are won by whoever's 
still standing at the end!</font>

61
00:07:01,210 --> 00:07:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you were a good person, 
but you're just an idiot.</font>

62
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not a bad philosophy, though.</font>

63
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall walk into the jaws 
of death with you, Stark.</font>

64
00:07:15,180 --> 00:07:20,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The more desperate the battle, the more 
catharsis you feel when you survive.</font>

65
00:07:20,970 --> 00:07:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm looking forward to that. 
I can't stop shaking.</font>

66
00:07:38,990 --> 00:07:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What should I do?</i></font>

67
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:47,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ms. Frieren disappeared at some point.</i></font>

68
00:07:51,660 --> 00:07:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nice to watch from afar 
once in a while.</font>

69
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's pointless trying 
to conceal your mana and hide.</font>

70
00:08:14,130 --> 00:08:17,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I created this fog with magic.</font>

71
00:08:17,850 --> 00:08:21,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can detect and identify targets 
from the faintest traces of mana.</font>

72
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No living creature can 
conceal their mana completely.</font>

73
00:08:35,860 --> 00:08:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Visibility is poor, 
and he's blocking my attacks.</i></font>

74
00:08:40,020 --> 00:08:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a bad matchup.</i></font>

75
00:08:57,830 --> 00:09:01,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I sense that Ms. Fern 
is struggling as well.</i></font>

76
00:09:02,210 --> 00:09:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's understandable.</i></font>

77
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her opponent seems to be a demon 
who uses unconventional magic.</i></font>

78
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Medrozobalt.</font>

79
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you looking at? 
I am your opponent.</font>

80
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:18,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

81
00:09:29,420 --> 00:09:32,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Meanwhile, my opponent is the
 opposite of "unconventional."</i></font>

82
00:09:32,820 --> 00:09:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her combat style is tried-and-tested.</i></font>

83
00:09:36,090 --> 00:09:39,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Defending even while she attacks.
 Her fundamentals are solid.</i></font>

84
00:09:40,210 --> 00:09:41,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She simply has no openings.</i></font>

85
00:09:42,660 --> 00:09:46,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mustn't face her head-on.</i></font>

86
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:56,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ideally, I'd work with Ms. Fern 
to bring both down,</i></font>

87
00:09:56,590 --> 00:10:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but this fog likely has powerful 
mana-detection capabilities.</i></font>

88
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Currently, Ms. Fern can't use stealth, 
her greatest asset.</i></font>

89
00:10:06,370 --> 00:10:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In which case, the situation would change 
greatly if this magic fog were removed.</i></font>

90
00:10:13,530 --> 00:10:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I cut loose a little?</font>

91
00:10:26,590 --> 00:10:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A flurry of blows?</i></font>

92
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her attack pattern changed!</i></font>

93
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:53,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I recognize this fighting style.</font>

94
00:10:53,970 --> 00:10:58,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's similar to one used by a clan that 
hunted demons on the Northern Plateau.</font>

95
00:10:59,730 --> 00:11:04,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An insane clan that dedicated 
their lives to killing demons.</font>

96
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How interesting.</font>

97
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This should be a good match.</font>

98
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:13,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's have a fair fight.</font>

99
00:11:21,430 --> 00:11:24,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's fast. I can't land any of my spells.</i></font>

100
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His masterful movements have become 
those of a savage predator.</i></font>

101
00:11:38,780 --> 00:11:42,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's still fighting despite the 
life-threatening wounds he's suffered.</i></font>

102
00:11:42,990 --> 00:11:47,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He has superhuman toughness 
and inexhaustible stamina.</i></font>

103
00:11:48,020 --> 00:11:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At this rate, he really will 
kill us through attrition.</i></font>

104
00:12:47,100 --> 00:12:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Genau, his swords have weakened!</font>

105
00:12:49,950 --> 00:12:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can break them!</font>

106
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed, he doesn't have the focus to 
maintain the mana in his swords anymore.</font>

107
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three to go!</font>

108
00:13:04,930 --> 00:13:06,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait.</i></font>

109
00:13:06,390 --> 00:13:08,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why does something feel off?</i></font>

110
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:13,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her attacks are ferocious, 
but I sense no bloodlust.</i></font>

111
00:13:14,330 --> 00:13:17,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you really are astute.</font>

112
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:21,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it took you too long to notice.</font>

113
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've just finished analyzing the fog.</font>

114
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those who only know how to fight 
only learn spells for combat.</font>

115
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any other member of my clan probably 
wouldn't have made it out of here.</font>

116
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I doubt they'd 
know how fun magic is.</font>

117
00:13:47,530 --> 00:13:49,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Erilfrachte.</font>

118
00:13:56,590 --> 00:13:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The fog cleared.</i></font>

119
00:13:58,980 --> 00:14:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How pointless.</i></font>

120
00:14:01,540 --> 00:14:04,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can simply create it again.</i></font>

121
00:14:09,010 --> 00:14:11,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did that girl go?</font>

122
00:14:22,910 --> 00:14:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hemmung's mana vanished.</i></font>

123
00:14:39,100 --> 00:14:41,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An attack? From where?</i></font>

124
00:14:55,270 --> 00:14:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zoltraak.</font>

125
00:15:00,970 --> 00:15:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's so far—</font>

126
00:15:12,050 --> 00:15:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A super-long-range attack from 
outside their detection radius</font>

127
00:15:15,530 --> 00:15:17,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">whose trajectory can't be predicted.</font>

128
00:15:18,010 --> 00:15:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad, Fern. I'm impressed.</font>

129
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:25,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd rather not fight a battle 
this difficult again.</font>

130
00:15:36,490 --> 00:15:37,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two to go!</font>

131
00:15:40,270 --> 00:15:41,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One!</font>

132
00:15:51,110 --> 00:15:53,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's over, Revolte.</font>

133
00:16:01,020 --> 00:16:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only humans think empty hands 
can't be weapons on their own.</font>

134
00:16:06,150 --> 00:16:10,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your fatal assumption was that I wouldn't 
be able to fight if you disarmed me.</font>

135
00:16:11,220 --> 00:16:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I win.</font>

136
00:16:14,180 --> 00:16:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our</i> fatal assumption? I think you'll find 
both humans and demons make those.</font>

137
00:16:19,940 --> 00:16:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For instance, you don't know 
how tenacious humans can be.</font>

138
00:16:35,850 --> 00:16:37,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cleaving Light!</font>

139
00:16:43,630 --> 00:16:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Digardnacht.</font>

140
00:17:03,950 --> 00:17:07,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem like a good person to me, too.</font>

141
00:17:08,610 --> 00:17:12,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're still trying to defend the village,
even after it's been destroyed.</font>

142
00:17:13,340 --> 00:17:15,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't do that.</font>

143
00:17:29,760 --> 00:17:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're still trying to save me.</font>

144
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it.</font>

145
00:17:39,870 --> 00:17:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a good guy after all.</font>

146
00:18:15,890 --> 00:18:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Methode.</font>

147
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:21,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I fail to die again?</font>

148
00:18:21,370 --> 00:18:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would seem that way.</font>

149
00:18:23,710 --> 00:18:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough. I can move again.</font>

150
00:18:30,350 --> 00:18:31,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How is Stark?</font>

151
00:18:31,630 --> 00:18:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a close call, but he'll survive.</font>

152
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I prioritized healing him over you.</font>

153
00:18:52,790 --> 00:18:54,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

154
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that displease you?</font>

155
00:18:56,020 --> 00:18:59,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. He did well.</font>

156
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Frieren's party will be staying 
in the village for a while.</font>

157
00:19:24,050 --> 00:19:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seems like I'm mostly better.</font>

158
00:19:27,870 --> 00:19:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's doing push-ups.</font>

159
00:19:29,500 --> 00:19:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could Mr. Stark possibly 
be a freak of nature?</font>

160
00:19:33,560 --> 00:19:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so mean.</font>

161
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I noticed your party 
doesn't have a priest.</font>

162
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be free for a while 
once this job is over.</font>

163
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I accompany you?</font>

164
00:19:47,040 --> 00:19:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Northern Plateau is dangerous 
without priest spells.</font>

165
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be fine.</font>

166
00:19:52,770 --> 00:19:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't cast anything high-level 
like healing magic,</font>

167
00:19:56,330 --> 00:19:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I know a few priest spells.</font>

168
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we find ourselves in serious trouble, 
we can always run away.</font>

169
00:20:03,860 --> 00:20:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what we've done until now.</font>

170
00:20:06,890 --> 00:20:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, we want to keep 
our priest slot open.</font>

171
00:20:12,680 --> 00:20:15,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We might see him again someday.</font>

172
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And...</font>

173
00:20:18,030 --> 00:20:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For some reason, Fern seems 
unhappy when you're around.</font>

174
00:20:21,980 --> 00:20:24,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my. I've made her hate me.</font>

175
00:20:25,380 --> 00:20:28,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I also love you, Ms. Fern.</font>

176
00:20:28,770 --> 00:20:31,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so cute when you're angry.</font>

177
00:20:32,090 --> 00:20:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Methode.</font>

178
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Chivalric Order of Norm have arrived.</font>

179
00:20:35,990 --> 00:20:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be accompanying 
them back to the south.</font>

180
00:20:40,750 --> 00:20:42,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

181
00:20:42,860 --> 00:20:45,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is where we say goodbye.</font>

182
00:20:47,130 --> 00:20:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stark, how are your injuries?</font>

183
00:20:51,070 --> 00:20:53,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All good. No problem.</font>

184
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

185
00:20:55,350 --> 00:20:57,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I owe you all a debt.</font>

186
00:20:57,830 --> 00:20:59,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One I intend to repay someday.</font>

187
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Genau.</font>

188
00:21:03,590 --> 00:21:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're forgetting something.</font>

189
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for your help.</font>

190
00:21:11,380 --> 00:21:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, thank you.</font>

191
00:21:13,110 --> 00:21:14,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope both of us live long lives.</font>

192
00:21:17,380 --> 00:21:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go.</font>

193
00:21:18,520 --> 00:21:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

194
00:21:20,150 --> 00:21:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you later.</font>

195
00:21:21,890 --> 00:21:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

196
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May our paths cross again.</font>

197
00:21:53,770 --> 00:21:56,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was it really the right move 
to turn her down?</font>

198
00:21:58,460 --> 00:22:00,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Methode, I mean.</font>

199
00:22:00,980 --> 00:22:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This party's priest is Sein.</font>

200
00:22:03,710 --> 00:22:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I mean she's a pretty older lady.</font>

201
00:22:07,390 --> 00:22:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't Sein complain 
when we see him again?</font>

202
00:22:10,830 --> 00:22:15,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who cares? This party 
already has an older lady.</font>

203
00:22:17,150 --> 00:22:18,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's true.</font>

204
00:22:20,900 --> 00:22:25,030
