205
00:23:50,100 --> 00:23:51,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll depend on the pay.</font>

206
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:54,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do dragons not normally travel in flights?</font>

207
00:23:51,380 --> 00:23:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That's some terrible luck.</font>

208
00:23:52,050 --> 00:23:54,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're the party of heroes.</font>

209
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:55,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm so bored, I could die.</font>

210
00:23:54,470 --> 00:23:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a tall order.</font>

211
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I've looked up to him since I was a child.</font>

212
00:23:56,490 --> 00:23:58,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's written in it?</font>

213
00:23:57,540 --> 00:23:59,990
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24">{\an8}<font color="#000000">Episode 37







Himmel's Memoirs</font></font>

214
00:23:58,200 --> 00:24:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Himmel's memoirs...</font>

